---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="服務項目 | ITUNG NAILS 伊特美甲" description="ITUNG NAILS 伊特美甲提供台北景美、新店地區平價高CP值凝膠美甲、手足保養、光療延甲與 nail art 設計。">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-8 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <nav class="text-sm text-it-text mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-it-cta">首頁</a> <span class="mx-2">/</span> <span>服務項目</span>
      </nav>
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">伊特美甲服務項目</h1>
        <p class="text-it-text max-w-2xl mx-auto">平價高CP值的專業美甲服務，讓小資族也能享受沙龍級品質。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">凝膠美甲</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">專業凝膠上色，色彩飽和持久。從單色、貓眼到漸層設計，滿足各種風格需求。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>單色凝膠</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$699 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>貓眼 / 漸層</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$899 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>設計款</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">依複雜度報價</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pricing" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">查看完整價格表 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">手足保養</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">深層滋養與角質護理，讓雙手雙足恢復細緻柔嫩。使用專業級保養產品。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>手部基礎保養</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$500</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>足部基礎保養</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$600</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>深層護理療程</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$900</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pricing" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">查看完整價格表 →</a>
        </div>
        <div id="extension" class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">光療延甲</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">改善甲型問題，打造完美長度與弧度。適合指甲較短或甲型不整者。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>單指延甲</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$100</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>全手延甲</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,000 起</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pricing" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">查看完整價格表 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">Nail Art 設計</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">從簡約線條到華麗手繪，依據您的風格量身設計。歡迎帶參考圖討論。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>簡單設計款</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,200 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>複雜設計款</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,800 起</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/gallery" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">看作品集 →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-it-text mb-4">* 以上價格僅供參考，實際價格依現場報價為準。</p>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/itung_lin_nails/" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-it-cta text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-it-cta/90 transition-colors">IG 私訊詢問最新價格</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
